Package jot.math.graph

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Converters
    Class that implements generic converters among graph data structures, e.g., array of pairs of nodes that form an edge 2 by 2 to a hash map with key pairs of the type <Node position, List of node neighbors>.
    Edge
    Class that implements an edge connecting to graph nodes.
    Node
    Class that implements a graph node for usage in path finders.
